An armed escort security officer is critically injured following a shooting while driving on Shamkwanga Street in Mamelodi on WednesdayOn arrival paramedics found the man lying in the driver s seat. Another service had already begun to extricate the man.&#8220;Paramedics assessed the man and found that he had sustained a gunshot wound to his chest and was in a critical condition,&#8221; said ER24 spokesperson Russel Meiring.The man was treated on the scene before being airlifted by a private medical helicopter to a nearby hospital for further care.It is believed that the man had been escorting a goods truck when an unknown number of gunmen opened fire.Local authorities are investigating the matter further.-TNA Reporter 